reviewText: Highly recommend this movie if you're looking for one with a lot of heart and charm. I still give this movie five stars even though the relationship between the lead male character and Sarah's boss was highly unlikely and not that believable. Sometimes a movie doesn't always have to be 100% believable for you to enjoy it. Seeing Sarah is worth it alone.
